### ===============================================
### RESERVAESTUDIO - FINANCEIRO STRIPE CONNECT (MVP)
### ===============================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@studioId = REPLACE_STUDIO_ID
@subscriberToken = REPLACE_SUBSCRIBER_TOKEN

### @name createConnectLink
POST {{baseUrl}}/financeiro/studios/{{studioId}}/stripe/connect
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}

### @name getConnectStatus
GET {{baseUrl}}/financeiro/studios/{{studioId}}/stripe/status?refresh=true
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}

### @name createDashboardLink
POST {{baseUrl}}/financeiro/studios/{{studioId}}/stripe/dashboard-link
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriberToken}}

### ❌ sem token
GET {{baseUrl}}/financeiro/studios/{{studioId}}/stripe/status
